.entry-header
Events at Blue Jacket's Gastropub
Nightly events available in Baldwin Park, FL
Taco Tuesday
Spice up your Tuesdays with our sizzling Taco Tuesday special!
Join us from 7:00 PM to 10:00 PM and indulge in the ultimate fiesta with our mouthwatering offer: $15 gets you 3 delicious tacos paired perfectly with a refreshing margarita!
Gather your friends and family for a flavor-packed evening of Mexican cuisine and festive drinks.
Happy Hour
Kick back and grab a drink after work with our Happy Hour deals.
Every Monday – Thursday, 4:00 – 7:00 PM
$6 IPA Draft Beer on Thursdays
Calling all craft beer enthusiasts!
Join us every Thursday night at Blue Jackets Gastropub for our IPA Draft Night! From 7:00 PM to 11:00 PM, enjoy the hoppy goodness of our handpicked selection of IPAs for just $6 per draft.
Whether you’re a seasoned IPA aficionado or curious to explore new flavors, our Thursday night special promises a brew-tiful experience for all.
Gather your friends, raise a glass, and savor the bold flavors of our premium IPAs.
DJ Too Tall
Blue Jacket’s Gastropub transforms into the ultimate destination every Friday night with DJ TooTall.
Sip on handcrafted cocktails, savor mouthwatering bites, and let the music carry you into the weekend.
Live Music
Get ready for a musical journey at Blue Jacket’s Gastropub! On select Saturdays of the month, we bring you live music that will make your evenings unforgettable.
Our talented musicians create the perfect atmosphere for a great night out.
Take advantage of this opportunity to dance the night away with great food and good company.
Saturday Night Karaoke
Hit the stage and unleash your inner superstar!
Join us on select Saturdays for karaoke night starting at 10:00 PM. Whether you’re a seasoned performer or a first-time singer, our karaoke event promises an unforgettable evening of music and entertainment.
Gather your friends, pick your favorite songs, and prepare to take center stage as you sing your heart out.
Football
Are you ready for some football?! Join us for Prime Time Football, where we have NFL games on the big screens – so you won’t miss a single play.
Or
Are you ready to for your college team to take it to the field? Catch all the action at Blue Jacket’s Gastropub!
Contact us for group rates at
bluejacketgastro@gmail.com
.
